item.title: CVE-2019-19345|2024-08-05T02:16:47.043Z -- %5Bunknown%5D -- openshift%2Fmediawiki-apb
item.description: A vulnerability was found in all openshift/mediawiki-apb 4.x.x versions prior to 4.3.0, where an insecure modification vulnerability in the /etc/passwd file was found in the container openshift/mediawiki-apb. An attacker with access to the container could use this flaw to modify /etc/passwd and escalate their privileges.
